Founder, leader, mentor, methodologist (Attracting investment, concept and methodology development, project management, team recruitment)

We developed a new online methodology to effectively develop a business initiative from scratch. The online concept proved to be more effective than the offline concepts. 
The whole acceleration process is fully digitized and allows participants to develop their own ideas and projects without being constantly guided an expert. 

The main points of the acceleration methodology are as follows: 
1.	Idea development based on cross-market analysis + use of digital marketing technologies like SemRush;
2.	Learning the theory of entrepreneurship;
3.	Rough packaging of the idea into a project;
4.	Text debates between participants on their projects based on BusinessChain technology;
5.	Modernization of projects;
6.	Impersonal feedback from experts (no mention of names, teams and projects);
7.	Continuation of textual debates on projects between participants with the use of critical comments of experts;
8.	Simultaneously all participants perform various challenges in the form of communication with potential clients, partners, competitors, investors, experts, documenting all their results. 
9.	The final packaging of the project on BusinessChain after several iterations: learning the theory, debates, expert feedback, completing challenges. 

Result: Participants become mentors for their own projects, are able to ask the most relevant questions about their projects, independently upgrade their projects and develop them (without waiting for anyone), finding the right partners, investors and colleagues.

